          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA",
                "ACTIV",
                "EXTB",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The stack was irradiated in a short Faraday-cup target",
                " holder at about 100 nA beam for 1.5 hours.",
                "The gamma spectrometric measurements of the individual",
                " foils were started several hours after the end of the",
                " irradiations.",
                "The beam intensity obtained via charge collection was",
                " corrected with the data from the monitor reactions.",
                "The analysis of the gamma spectra was done in two",
                " steps: an initial automatic mode provided by the",
                " analysis software followed by an interactive peak",
                " fitting and separation manual mode."
              ]
            }
          ],
